OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1774440171
OL,3,COne of London's busiest roads, the A40
OL,4,CWestway, closed more than a month
OL,6,FDrivers are being warned the closure
OL,7,Fof one of London's busiest roads for
OL,8,Fmore than a month will have a
OL,9,F"significant impact".
OL,11,FTransport for London (TfL) issued the
OL,12,Falert as it starts major work on a two-
OL,13,Fand-a-half mile stretch of the A40
OL,14,Fbetween the Westway roundabout and the
OL,15,FMarylebone flyover.
OL,17,FThe elevated dual carriageway is a
OL,18,Fmajor route for people travelling to
OL,19,Fand from the west of the capital, and
OL,20,Fis used by up to 96,000 vehicles a day.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@TO]
