PN,40802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1774440171
OL,3,COne of London's busiest roads, the A40
OL,4,CWestway, closed more than a month
OL,6,FRenewal works on the A40 have been
OL,7,Fcarried out for several years, but TfL
OL,8,Fsaid it must close until "late April".
OL,10,FThis is to enable the replacement of
OL,11,Ftwo joints which allow it to safely
OL,12,Fexpand and contract with temperature
OL,13,Fchanges and vehicle movements.
OL,15,FTfL insisted it "reviewed a range of
OL,16,Foptions" but concluded that the full
OL,17,Fmulti-week closure was "the best way
OL,18,Fto ensure essential work is completed
OL,19,Fas quickly and safely as possible".
OL,26,@pD@ZOUpD@eO]wD@QOUxD@HO]yD@XOU{D@bO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
