OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1774440171
OL,3,COne of London's busiest roads, the A40
OL,4,CWestway, closed more than a month
OL,6,FTransport analytics company Inrix
OL,7,Fidentified a nearby stretch of the A40
OL,8,Fas London's most congested road
OL,9,Fcorridor in 2024, with drivers who
OL,10,Fused it at 5pm each day spending an
OL,11,Festimated 68 hours sitting in traffic
OL,12,Fover the year.
OL,14,FTfL said: "Though every effort will be
OL,15,Fmade to reduce disruption, TfL
OL,16,Frecognises the closure will have a
OL,17,Fsignificant impact on road users.
OL,26,@vD@KOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
