OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1774440171
OL,3,COne of London's busiest roads, the A40
OL,4,CWestway, closed more than a month
OL,6,F"A comprehensive traffic signal
OL,7,Fstrategy will be put in place to keep
OL,8,Ftraffic moving as smoothly as possible
OL,9,Fduring the closure."
OL,11,FDiversion routes will be signposted
OL,12,Fbut journeys are "likely to be
OL,13,Fdelayed", TfL added.
OL,15,FStuart Harvey, TfL's chief capital
OL,16,Fofficer, said: "It's vital that we
OL,17,Fensure the A40 flyover is well
OL,18,Fmaintained for the tens of thousands
OL,19,Fof people who use it each day.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@TO]tD@ROUuD@HO]xD@POU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/5
