OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1774440171
OL,3,COne of London's busiest roads, the A40
OL,4,CWestway, closed more than a month
OL,6,F"This essential work will allow the
OL,7,Fflyover to continue to be used safely.
OL,9,F"We appreciate that, though necessary,
OL,10,Fthese works will cause disruption to
OL,11,Fjourneys, and I'd like to thank people
OL,12,Fin the area for their patience.
OL,14,F"I'd encourage everyone to plan ahead
OL,15,Fand use alternative modes of transport
OL,16,Fwhere possible."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUvD@AOUxD@PO]
